### Змінні
@host = http://localhost:8080
@api = {{host}}/api/products

### ==================== CREATE (POST) ====================

### Створити продукт 1 - Ноутбук
POST {{api}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Ноутбук",
  "description": "Lenovo ThinkPad X1 Carbon Gen 11",
  "price": 35000.00,
  "quantity": 10
}

